<div class="item-page">
	<h1>
	Careers	</h1>


	<ul class="actions">
						<li class="print-icon">
			<a href="/en/careers?tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;page=" title="Print" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','status=no,toolbar=no,scrollbars=yes,titlebar=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480,directories=no,location=no'); return false;" rel="nofollow"><img src="/media/system/images/printButton.png" alt="Print"  /></a>			</li>
		
					<li class="email-icon">
			<a href="/en/component/mailto/?tmpl=component&amp;template=fuelquest2009&amp;link=5c152a593cff3dcde26c736b432f3514b905b5fb" title="Email" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','width=400,height=350,menubar=yes,resizable=yes'); return false;"><img src="/media/system/images/emailButton.png" alt="Email"  /></a>			</li>
		
		
	
	</ul>







<p><img class="floatRight imgBorderWhite" src="/images/stories/img_careers.jpg" alt="img_careers" height="140" width="245" />FuelQuest, a JMP Securities "Hot 100: The Best Privately Held Software Companies" selection in 2011 and 2012, provides on-demand fuel management, tax automation, and compliance solutions for suppliers, distributors, buyers, and traders of petroleum products and other energy commodities.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>FuelQuest is a high performance work culture that encourages and fosters innovation and excellence. We are looking for candidates who excel in what they do and are looking for an environment that provides the challenges and opportunities to do their best work and have fun while doing it. We have a variety of positions available for experienced professionals. Not only are we the global leader in fuel management and tax automation, we are also one of the fastest growing companies in the region. We offer you the opportunity to work on cutting-edge technology and utilize best practice business processes.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We offer an outstanding package of benefits including competitive salaries; fully paid health, dental, vision and life insurance; 401(K) plan and a high tech, fun, energetic environment. There are opportunities where no travel is required and others where extensive travel is available.</p> 
	
</div>
</div>
                                         
